## Stack

- **Backend:** Python 3, FastAPI, Pydantic v2, SQLAlchemy 2 (`Mapped[...]`, `DeclarativeBase`), SQLite in dev
- **Frontend:** TypeScript, React 18, Vite, Tailwind CSS (see `frontend/`)
- **Docs:** MkDocs from root `mkdocs.yml` (`docs/`)

## Authoritative style rules

- **`.cursor/rules/code-style.mdc`** — formatting (Black, isort), types, privacy, Pydantic at boundaries
- **`.cursor/rules/doc-standards.mdc`** — docstrings, Mermaid, tie-backs to `docs/design/`
- **`.editorconfig`** and **`pyproject.toml`** — line length, indent

## Tests and quality

- pytest; coverage targets in **`.cursorrules`** (≥80% overall; stricter for business logic)
- Run from repo root per `pyproject.toml` / CI

Keep this file **free of product domain** except pointers to design docs as in **doc-standards**.
